   version stable 0.12.1 0.11.13 0.11.12
   require flex libtool ncurses openssl readline zlib
  optional docbook-xml-4.1.2 ''            --without-docbook                   to generate HTML manuals
  optional openldap          --enable-ldap '--disable-ldap --disable-ldap-ssl' to enable use of LDAP for authentication
      opts --without-pam  --enable-static=no
  category security
 attribute console library makej multilib-concurrent
